1
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:43,520
The deceased was hacked to death.

2
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,960
The body has begun to decompose.

3
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,400
The time of death was over five days ago.

4
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,760
The murder weapon was a common knife.

5
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:54,480
There is nothing special about it.

6
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:57,480
Five days.

7
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,640
That was before Miaoling's coffin was lifted.

8
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,080
This case is becoming more intriguing.

9
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,680
The deceased's body is missing...

10
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,280
...yet an extra male corpse has appeared.

11
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:09,840
My Lord.

12
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,200
The identity of the male corpse has been confirmed.

13
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:13,920
It is Zhu Zi, the helper at Anyefang Coffin Shop.

14
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:14,680
I see.

15
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:16,920
In that case...

16
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:19,600
...it explains the strange movements in the coffin.

17
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:31,680
Zhu Zi must have discovered a dark secret.

18
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,680
So the killer silenced him.

19
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,240
To cover it up...

20
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:37,440
...they hid him inside the coffin.

21
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:44,320
But Zhu Zi wasn't dead when stuffed inside.

22
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,600
When he woke up and tried to push open the lid...

23
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:48,560
...he found it being held down tight.

24
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,320
He eventually succumbed to his injuries inside.

25
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,080
Help!

26
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,320
Help!

27
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:02,960
Help!

28
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:08,160
Brother Dongqiu!

29
00:02:08,480 --> 00:02:08,880
Help!

30
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,360
What's going on?

31
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,960
Don't ask me, I don't know!

32
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,440
Hold it down tight!

33
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,000
Let's pretend we know nothing.

34
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:17,720
Let's go.

35
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,000
So...

36
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,920
The deaths of Wu Tuan, his wife, and Zhu Zi...

37
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,280
...are all connected to that Paper effigy.

38
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:29,800
Who swapped Miaoling's body for the Paper effigy...

39
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,600
...is the key to this case.

40
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,560
It was Zhao Di.

41
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:35,520
No.

42
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,320
Zhao Di was eager to bury Miaoling quickly...

43
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,560
...to avoid any complications.

44
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:40,600
Why?

45
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,520
Follow me.

46
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,040
Why the rush? Wait for me!

47
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:07,560
Luckily, Shentu Baiqi, you are The Greatest Detective of the Uncanny...

48
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,720
...and not a criminal.

49
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,120
Otherwise, with your skills...

50
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,600
...if you wanted to commit a crime...

51
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,960
...for this Vice Minister to catch you...

52
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:16,920
...would be no easy task.

53
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:17,280
Careful.

54
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:18,760
That is highly poisonous.

55
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,200
Why didn't you say so earlier?

56
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,080
Everything in my room is lethal.

57
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,160
But don't worry.

58
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,280
You won't die while I'm here.

59
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,200
If I do die...

60
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,160
...I'll haunt you as a ghost.

61
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:32,280
Is that so?

62
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,360
Then smell this.

63
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:46,480
This is...

64
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,960
the scent from Miaoling's room.

65
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,040
Precisely.

66
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,440
This incense is called Fatal Fragrance.

67
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,200
It comes from the Western Regions and is extremely rare.

68
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,480
Although not highly toxic,

69
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,960
if mixed into incense and inhaled over a long period,

70
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,200
it causes depression at best,

71
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,120
and at worst,

72
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,000
it can be fatal.

73
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,320
In that case,

74
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,720
it was Zhao Di who killed his wife, Miaoling.

75
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,000
Exactly.

76
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,480
The Sun family is wealthy.

77
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,680
Zhao Di, the live-in son-in-law,

78
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:14,920
used this very incense

79
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,320
to kill Miaoling without anyone knowing.

80
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,200
To the outside world,

81
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:22,240
he claimed Miaoling was frail

82
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,120
and died of illness.

83
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,680
He planned that after burying Miaoling,

84
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,640
he would seize the Sun family fortune.

85
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,160
All of this

86
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,360
should have been seamless.

87
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,240
But someone was secretly watching,

88
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,120
stole the body,

89
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,240
and replaced it with a paper effigy for the burial.

90
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,960
So this person likely knows

91
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,240
the truth about Miaoling's death.

92
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,000
I fear they intend

93
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,160
to avenge her.

94
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,720
Now that we know his objective,

95
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,200
there is a way to make him show his hand.

96
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:58,560
Hmm?

97
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:07,680
Is there something on my face?

98
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,480
Why are you staring at me?

99
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,320
It's giving me the creeps.

100
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:12,920
Well,

101
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,600
naturally, I need to borrow

102
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,360
the Vice Minister's skilled hands.

103
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:26,800
My Lord,

104
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:29,400
will this really help find my daughter's body?

105
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,440
Now that Zhao Di is missing,

106
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,720
as long as we can find him,

107
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:33,960
the cause of Miaoling's death

108
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,240
will come to light.

109
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,520
What?

110
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,480
What do you mean by that, My Lord?

111
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:39,120
Could it be

112
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,880
that my daughter did not die of illness?

113
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:42,520
No...

114
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,760
Master, My Lord,

115
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,840
the pallbearers have arrived.

116
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,360
Understood.

117
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,160
Go on.

118
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,520
My condolences, Master.

119
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,000
Everyone,

120
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,040
my son-in-law

121
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,320
has met an unfortunate and violent end.

122
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,920
The burial is tomorrow.

123
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,720
I know you are all reliable workers.

124
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:36,480
I entrust the funeral procession to you tomorrow.

125
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:40,120
It is our blessing to be looked after by you, Master.

126
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,320
You can rest assured about everything.

127
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,040
Right, Brother Dongqiu?

128
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:46,640
Yes.

129
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,080
This isn't exactly a deposit,

130
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,360
just a small token from this old man.

131
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,200
I hope you will take great care.

132
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,080
Thank you, Master.

133
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,720
Thank you, Master.

134
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:03,760
Thank you, Master.

135
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:05,960
Well?

136
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,120
Your method really worked.

137
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:10,920
Last night,

138
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,920
staying up all night wasn't in vain.

139
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,080
Follow him.

140
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,280
Don't worry.

141
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,480
It's already arranged.

142
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:20,640
Lady Xiaomu...

143
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:21,840
You...

144
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,440
Mu Guiyi is one of my people.

145
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,120
You agreed to this.

146
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,040
Why would he come here?
